					<h2>The Beginners Guide to Saving and Investing for Canadians</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text">
<p>The Beginners Guide to Saving and Investing for Canadians is just that &#8211; a primer for those just getting started with saving and investing.  No complicated technical treatments, just 100 pages of easy to understand guidance on saving and investing.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s uniquely Canadian perspective means you&#8217;ll learn about things that are important to Canadians.  RRSP&#8217;s, RESP&#8217;s, and Canadian investments are all explained in a fashion that&#8217;s easy to understand for consumers just starting out.  </p>
<p>Rather than having a book written by a generalist, this book has 5 chapters each written by a specialist in the field.  We&#8217;ve collected 5 of the top online bloggers and authorities and had them write a chapter on their area of expertise.  So while you&#8217;re getting a beginner&#8217;s overview, you&#8217;re also getting it from someone who&#8217;s an expert on the subject.</p>
